Title: iPhone 12, 6.1 Inches,Smartphone,Fully Unlocked,Like New,With Original Packaging (White, 64GB)
Description:
Product description    
 iPhone 12 comes with a 6.1-inch OLED display, 5nm A14 Bionic processor, and a dual-camera setup with a large sensor. 5G and Face ID are also standard features along with True Tone support for adjusting the white balance to the ambient lighting, and wide color support for true-to-life colors. The iPhone 12 is available in six different colors: White, Black, , (PRODUCT)RED, Purple, Blue and Green.
